title: MagicISO Maker 5.4 Build 256 Patch Only ~ Team ZOiT
description:
Download MagicISO Maker 5.4 Build 256 from http://www.magiciso.com/download.htm, install, DO NOT Run! Copy and overwrite files in the MagicISO program folder (C:Program FilesMagicISO) titled "miso" and "MagicISO" with the ones in this folder, then merge "MagicISO.reg" (also in this folder) with the windows registry (you should be able to do this by double clicking on the file). Now you can run MagicISO.
